    <p class="lede">
        MDArea is a <code>textarea</code> augmentation that adds a toolbar and keyboard shortcuts to any textarea to turn it into a lightweight markdown editor.
    </p>

    <textarea rows="10" placeholder="Markdown goes in here">
### SpaceX
**Space Exploration Technologies Corp. (SpaceX)** is an American aerospace manufacturer, space transportation services and communications corporation headquartered in Hawthorne, California. SpaceX was founded in 2002 by [Elon Musk](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elon_Musk) with the goal of reducing space transportation costs to enable the colonization of Mars. SpaceX:
- manufactures the Falcon 9 and Falcon Heavy launch vehicles
- several rocket engines
- Dragon cargo amd crew spacecraft
- Starlink communications satellites.
    </textarea>

    <section>
        <h2>Installation</h2>
        <p>Install via NPM</p>
{% highlight "bash" %}
npm install github:bemky/mdarea
{% endhighlight %}
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Import and Initialize</h2>
{% highlight "js" %}
import MDArea from 'mdarea';

new MDArea(document.querySelector('textarea'));
{% endhighlight %}
        <p>
            MDArea will also render its own textarea if not given one. Instead it can take an object where each key is an attribute of the textarea.
        </p>
{% highlight "js" %}
import MDArea from 'mdarea';

const area = new MDArea({
    name: "building[details]",
    rows: 10
});
document.append(area.el);
{% endhighlight %}
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Style</h2>
        <p>The MDArea will take on the style of the textarea. It reads the style attributes on render and applies attributes via CSS variables.</p>

        <div class="example-grid">
            <div>
                <textarea class="example-1" rows="8">Styled textarea</textarea>
            </div>
            <div>
{% highlight "html" %}
<textarea class="example-1" rows="8">Styled textarea</textarea>
{% endhighlight %}
{% highlight "css" %}
.example-1 {
    background: rgba(240, 237, 255, 1.000);
    border-radius: 0.75em;
    border-color: rgba(223, 199, 255, 1.000);
    color: rgba(108, 51, 186, 1.000);
    width: 100%;
    padding: 2em;
}
{% endhighlight %}
            </div>
        </div>
